name: Global Resell Business
overview: Founded in 2006, Global Resell Business dedicatedly to distributing laptop parts and IC components to global market. As a leading distributor in China, Global Resell Business is able to provide wide range of in-stocks laptop parts including LCD, HDD, Keyboard, AC Adapter, Batteries, Hard Drive, Optical Disk Drive, Memory, Motherboard, CPU and IC components with original manufacture quality and wholesale price. With its 5 years experiences in the field of distribution and electronic market, we has established a solid supply networks from world well-known to local major distributors and manufactures especially in Asia area.
